# Boss-Core Changelog

All notable changes to the boss-core module are documented here.
The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/), and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [1.0.0] - 2021-04-25

### Added

- CHANGELOG
- User entity
- User type
- NoSuchUser exception
- UserAlreadyExists exception
- User repository
- User service
- Api request response transfer object
- Register user input transfer object
- Register user output transfer object
- Secure user details transfer object
- Update user input transfer object
- tests for each added object

## [1.1.0] - 2021-05-03

### Added

- Card Entity
- Card Repository
- Card Type
- Confirmation Entity
- Confirmation Repository
- Confirmation Service
- Confirmation Type
- Loan Entity
- Loan Repository
- Loan Type
- Password Configuration

### Changed

- User created and deleted from DATETIME to long
- User changes reflected in all classes which use it or replicate its data

## [1.2.0] - 2021-05-13

### Added

- Account Entity
- Account Holder Entity
- Account Type
- Account Holder Repository
- Transaction Entity
- Transaction Type
